{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8d2c65a307","title":"参战主力集结休整未使用之部队相机齐灭东明之敌一部","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b27b19e905","index":0,"year":1946,"month":9,"day":7,"articleId":"8d2c65a307"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0551472463","type":"paragraph","text":"参战主力集结休整未使用之部队","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"8d2c65a307"},{"id":"665a3da8ca","type":"paragraph","text":"相机齐灭东明之敌一部","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"8d2c65a307"},{"id":"46e4ec6e7a","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年9月7日）刘、邓：","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"8d2c65a307"},{"id":"bf99e11951","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）鱼玄电悉，甚慰。庆祝你们歼灭第三师的大胜利，望传令全军嘉奖。（二）敌人尚有进攻力量，我军此次参战主力立即集结休整补充，准备再战，申齐起十天内休补完毕。（三）以尚未使用之部队相机歼灭东明方面敌之一部，并相机占领考城，收复东明：以地方部队深入敌后活动，抚击敌人。（四）你们现在兵力配备，人数，枪数，主官姓名，战力强弱，股告。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"8d2c65a307"},{"id":"da69b6f4cd","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"8d2c65a307"},{"id":"f73fb3b0fd","type":"paragraph","text":"申虎午[]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给晋冀鲁豫野战军司令员刘伯承和政治委员邓小平的电报。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"8d2c65a307"}],"page":{"id":"7788830913","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"8d2c65a307","start":139,"end":139}}}},"__N_SSG":true}